# Styling & SSR

## Semantic tokens only

Use: `text-foreground`, `bg-primary`, `border-border`, `bg-sidebar`, `text-muted-foreground`.

Never: `gray-500`, `red-600`, `neutral-*`, arbitrary hex in components.

## CSS variables (critical)

Theme tokens are defined in **two places** - keep them in sync:

1. `packages/ui/src/components/ui/gluestack-ui-provider/config.ts`
2. `packages/ui/src/styles/globals.css` (`:root` and `.dark`)

GluestackUIProvider injects vars client-side. Without `globals.css` vars, first paint shows unstyled buttons and sidebar (FOUC).

## Tailwind

- Config: `packages/ui/tailwind.config.cjs`
- Web app extends UI config + scans both packages in `apps/web/tailwind.config.cjs`
- Prefer component `variant` / `size` props over redundant `className`

## Global button fixes

`globals.css` includes targeted rules for solid primary/destructive/secondary buttons. Subtle destructive actions should use `variant="ghost"` + `bg-destructive/10`, not solid `bg-destructive`.

## Layout height

Prefer `min-h-dvh` over `min-h-screen` for full-viewport auth/app shells.
